dsDescriptionValue.value:
This dataset contains files relevant to analyses carried out during the revision process of the associated manuscript.

In order to preserve the nested file structure (which is what is used by the scripts to separate scripts, data, output, etc), the nested folder structures are comparessed as tar.gz files. When you open one of these files, it should reproduce the internal folder structure.

At the time this dataset was created, Dataverse did not support nested file structures directly, unfortunately (see discussion here), so the tar.gz structure is a workaround.

files.description:
Compressed file containing code, some data, and model outputs for the trial-level mixed models associated with Revision 1 of the manuscript at Cortex.
File and directory descriptions are contained in the README.html file in the root directory.

These files are also available at https://github.com/dstanner/Academic/tree/master/Cortex%20Trial%20Analysis
files.label: TrialAnalysisCortexRev1.tar.gz
